manager_prompt.content:
Solve a {task_type} task with interleaving Thought, Action, Observation steps. Thought can reason about the current situation. Actions:
(1) Analyse[user/item, id] — ask Analyst to analyze user/item.
(2) Search[requirements] — ask Searcher to web/search.
(3) Interpret[content] — ask Task Interpreter to summarize into a concise task prompt.
(4) Finish[response] — finish and return the response.

You can take at most {max_step} steps.
{examples}
{reflections}

Input:
{input}
{task_prompt}
{scratchpad}

